## 7. Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|--------|-----------|
| Planning Center/Breeze launch competing feature | Medium | High | Move fast MVP; own "flexible workflows" + "standalone option"; consider acquisition. |
| ChMS integration APIs break | Low | Medium | Maintain CSV fallback; monitor API docs; version-lock dependencies. |
| Beta churches churn (feature mismatch) | Low | Low | Weekly feedback loops; prioritize their pain; iterate fast. (Workflow flexibility helps here) |
| Pricing too high / free tier abused | Low | Low | Monitor LTV/CAC; adjust tiers if needed; add validation. |
| Market too niche | Low | Medium | Horizontal pivot early; "volunteer calendar" messaging broader than "scheduling". |
| Workflow flexibility adds complexity | Medium | Medium | MVP launches with 1 workflow mode (Centralized); others added incrementally based on feedback. |

